com.sap.cloud.sdk.s4hana.datamodel.odata.services

Interface SupplierActivityService

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultSupplierActivityService

    public interface SupplierActivityService

    This communication scenario enables a remote system to read Supplier Activities from or in SAP S/4HANA tenant. The remote system calls the synchronous OData Service API_SUPPLIER_ACTIVITY.

    Reference: SAP API Business Hub

    Details:

    OData Service:API_SUPPLIER_ACTIVITY_SRV
    API Version:1
    Minimum ERP Version:1708
    Communication Scenario:Supplier Activity Integration (SAP_COM_0137)
    Scope Items:Business Partner for Treasury and Risk Management (19C)
